# Arkas, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Arkas (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Buynaksky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. The population was 1,676 as of 2010. There are 5 streets.
Geography
Arkas is located 25&nbsp;km south of Buynaksk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Arykhkent is the nearest rural locality.
